KSword Booting Tab Plugin 1.0.1

This plugin is an independent, process-isolated KSword plugin. It is not part
of the KSword main repository or KSword release payload.

The packaged plugin redistributes the unmodified official HackBGRT 2.6.0
Windows release:

  Upstream: https://github.com/Metabolix/HackBGRT
  Release: v2.6.0 (2026-04-02)
  Archive: HackBGRT-2.6.0.zip
  Archive SHA-256:
  6204911D777AC03E514B90126568EF6FAA1D477779B31C536B142DBA92F4A2C0

HackBGRT is licensed under the MIT License. Its original LICENSE is retained
under HackBGRT/LICENSE. The redistributed shim/MokManager files carry separate
copyright information retained under HackBGRT/shim-signed/COPYRIGHT.

The plugin does not modify HackBGRT executables or EFI binaries. It writes a
configuration and image in a per-user working copy, and invokes only the
documented batch interface. It intentionally does not expose HackBGRT's legacy
Windows boot-loader overwrite command.
